          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>The Original Steak</strong><br/>Rice, refried beans, onion & cilantro.<br/><strong>14.99</strong></p><p><strong>Chelas Burrito</strong><br/>Black beans, sour cream, guacamole, cabbage, onion, cilantro, Monterey jack cheese.<br/><strong>Chicken or Carnitas 15.99</strong><br/><strong>Steak 16.99</strong></p><p><strong>Grilled Ribeye</strong><br/>Chipotle BBQ rib-eye steak, sour cream, guacamole, cabbage, onion, cilantro, Monterey jack cheese.<br/><strong>17.99</strong></p><p><strong>El Macho</strong><br/>Steak and chicken, refried beans, rice, guacamole, cabbage, onion, cilantro, Monterey jack cheese.<br/><strong>16.99</strong></p><p><strong>Chicken Fajita</strong><br/>Sautéed red bell peppers, onions, black beans & Monterey jack cheese.<br/><strong>15.99</strong></p><p><strong>Chile Verde Wet</strong><br/>Our Famous Chile Verde Carnitas with rice, refried beans, melted Colby jack cheese, sour cream.<br/><strong>16.99</strong></p><p><strong>Bean & Cheese</strong><br/>Refried beans & Colby jack cheese.<br/><strong>10.99</strong></p><p><strong>1925 Don Ole</strong><br/>Steak, papas fritas, Colby jack cheese, guacamole, black beans, pico de gallo.<br/><strong>15.99</strong></p><p><strong>Baja Burrito</strong><br/>Steak, shrimp, cabbage, pico de gallo, chipotle crème, avocado slices.<br/><strong>17.99</strong></p><p><strong>Laguna Fish Burrito</strong><br/>Beer battered or grilled fish, Monterey jack cheese, cabbage, pico de gallo, avocado slices, chipotle crème.<br/><strong>16.99</strong></p>"
