          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Rib Eye Tacos</strong><br/><em>Voted Best of O.C.</em><br/>Chipotle BBQ rib-eye steak, Mexican lime slaw, chipotle crème, pickled red onions & queso fresco.<br/><strong>17.99</strong></p><p><strong>•</strong></p><p><strong>La Calle Tacos</strong><br/>Authentic Mexican street tacos.<br/>Corn tortillas filled with your choice of mean and topped with onion & cilantro. <br/><strong>Chicken, Carnitas or Steak</strong> <br/><strong>13.99</strong></p><p><strong>•</strong></p><p><strong>Crispy Tacos</strong><br/><strong>Chicken </strong>(most popular). <strong>14.99<br/>Shredded Beef </strong>Corn tortilla with lettuce, sour cream, Colby jack cheese. <strong>15.99<br/>Carnitas or Potato </strong>Corn tortilla with lettuce, pico, queso fresco <strong>14.99</strong></p><p><strong>•</strong></p><p><strong>La Gringa Tacos</strong><br/>Flour tortilla, your choice of meat, guacamole, sour cream, cabbage, onion, cilantro, Monterey jack cheese.<br/><strong>Chicken or Carnitas 16.50</strong><br/><strong>Steak 16.99</strong></p><p><strong>•</strong></p><p><strong>Beer Battered Fish Tacos</strong><br/>Pacifico® battered white fish, Monterey jack cheese, cabbage, pico de gallo, chipotle crème sauce.<br/><strong>15.99</strong></p><p><strong>•</strong></p><p><strong>Shrimp Tacos</strong><br/>Corn tortillas, cabbage, pico de gallo, chipotle crème, avocado slices.<br/><strong>17.99</strong></p>"
